      <![CDATA[<h2 id="一、安装-Docker-Ubuntu-22-04"><a href="#一、安装-Docker-Ubuntu-22-04" class="headerlink" title="一、安装 Docker (Ubuntu 22.04)"></a>一、安装 Docker (Ubuntu 22.04)</h2><h3 id="1-安装依赖"><a href="#1-安装依赖" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装依赖"></a>1. 安装依赖</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install ca-certificates curl -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-添加-Docker-软件源（清华镜像）"><a href="#2-添加-Docker-软件源（清华镜像）" class="headerlink" title="2. 添加 Docker 软件源（清华镜像）"></a>2. 添加 Docker 软件源（清华镜像）</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建密钥存储目录</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo install -m 0755 -d /etc/apt/keyrings</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 下载 Docker GPG 密钥</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo curl -fsSL https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/docker-ce/linux/ubuntu/gpg -o /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.asc</span><br><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">chmod</span> a+r /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.asc</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 添加 Docker 源</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;deb [arch=<span class="subst">$(dpkg --print-architecture)</span> signed-by=/etc/apt/keyrings/docker.asc] https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/docker-ce/linux/ubuntu <span class="subst">$(. /etc/os-release &amp;&amp; echo <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$VERSION_CODENAME</span>&quot;</span>)</span> stable&quot;</span> | sudo <span class="built_in">tee</span> /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list &gt; /dev/null</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-安装-Docker"><a href="#3-安装-Docker" class="headerlink" title="3. 安装 Docker"></a>3. 安装 Docker</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 1. 更新软件源</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 2. 安装 Docker</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io docker-buildx-plugin docker-compose-plugin -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-启动并配置"><a href="#4-启动并配置" class="headerlink" title="4. 启动并配置"></a>4. 启动并配置</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 启动 Docker 服务</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl start docker</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> docker</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将当前用户加入 docker 组（免 sudo 运行）</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo usermod -aG docker <span class="variable">$USER</span></span><br><span class="line">newgrp docker   <span class="comment"># 立即生效</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-配置镜像加速器（可选，但强烈推荐）"><a href="#5-配置镜像加速器（可选，但强烈推荐）" class="headerlink" title="5. 配置镜像加速器（可选，但强烈推荐）"></a>5. 配置镜像加速器（可选，但强烈推荐）</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">mkdir</span> -p /etc/docker</span><br><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">tee</span> /etc/docker/daemon.json &lt;&lt;<span class="string">EOF</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">  &quot;registry-mirrors&quot;: [</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    &quot;https://docker.mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn&quot;,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    &quot;https://docker.m.daocloud.io&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">  ]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">EOF</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 重启 Docker</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl daemon-reload</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl restart docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-验证安装"><a href="#6-验证安装" class="headerlink" title="6. 验证安装"></a>6. 验证安装</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker --version</span><br><span class="line">docker compose version</span><br><span class="line">docker run hello-world</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>看到 <code>Hello from Docker!</code> 即表示安装成功。</p><hr><h2 id="二、安装-Docker-可视化管理界面-Portainer"><a href="#二、安装-Docker-可视化管理界面-Portainer" class="headerlink" title="二、安装 Docker 可视化管理界面 (Portainer)"></a>二、安装 Docker 可视化管理界面 (Portainer)</h2><h3 id="1-存储卷（Volume）操作"><a href="#1-存储卷（Volume）操作" class="headerlink" title="1. 存储卷（Volume）操作"></a>1. 存储卷（Volume）操作</h3><p>存储卷是 Docker 用来保存数据的“硬盘”，即使更新或重建容器，数据也不会丢失。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看所有数据卷</span></span><br><span class="line">docker volume <span class="built_in">ls</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建一个名为 my_data 的卷</span></span><br><span class="line">docker volume create my_data</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看某个卷的详细信息（如存储路径）</span></span><br><span class="line">docker volume inspect my_data</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-安装-Portainer"><a href="#2-安装-Portainer" class="headerlink" title="2. 安装 Portainer"></a>2. 安装 Portainer</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run -d -p 8000:8000 -p 9000:9000 --name=portainer --restart=always -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock -v portainer_data:/data portainer/portainer-ce</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>访问地址：<code>http://192.168.5.14:9000</code></li><li>通过浏览器访问使用图形化管理工具<h3 id="3-注册-Portainer"><a href="#3-注册-Portainer" class="headerlink" title="3. 注册 Portainer"></a>3. 注册 Portainer</h3></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 重启容器生成新令牌</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo docker restart portainer</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 获取最新令牌</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo docker logs portainer 2&gt;&amp;1 | grep <span class="string">&quot;setup_token=&quot;</span> | <span class="built_in">tail</span> -1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>用新令牌在网页上继续初始化即可。</p><hr><h2 id="三、部署-Nextcloud-个人网盘"><a href="#三、部署-Nextcloud-个人网盘" class="headerlink" title="三、部署 Nextcloud 个人网盘"></a>三、部署 Nextcloud 个人网盘</h2><h3 id="1-在-Portainer-中创建容器"><a href="#1-在-Portainer-中创建容器" class="headerlink" title="1. 在 Portainer 中创建容器"></a>1. 在 Portainer 中创建容器</h3><pre><code>姓名图片输入一样的即可</code></pre><ul><li><strong>端口映射</strong>：主机 <code>8080</code> → 容器 <code>80</code></li><li><strong>数据持久化</strong>：<code>/var/www/html</code> → <code>/home/guzihan/Downloads/NextCloud</code></li><li><strong>重启策略</strong>：选择 <code>always</code><h3 id="2-更新-DNS-配置"><a href="#2-更新-DNS-配置" class="headerlink" title="2. 更新 DNS 配置"></a>2. 更新 DNS 配置</h3></li></ul><p>访问 <code>ip:9000</code>，修改 <code>config/config.php</code>，添加完成后重启即可。</p><hr><h2 id="四、Nextcloud-文件同步管理"><a href="#四、Nextcloud-文件同步管理" class="headerlink" title="四、Nextcloud 文件同步管理"></a>四、Nextcloud 文件同步管理</h2><h3 id="1-手动执行文件扫描"><a href="#1-手动执行文件扫描" class="headerlink" title="1. 手动执行文件扫描"></a>1. 手动执行文件扫描</h3><p>如果新文件未在网页端显示，需要进入容器执行扫描。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进入 Nextcloud 容器</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo docker <span class="built_in">exec</span> -it nextcloud bash</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 如果容器名字不同，先用 docker ps 查一下</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 执行文件扫描命令,同步新文件到数据库</span></span><br><span class="line">php occ files:scan --all</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 退出容器</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">exit</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-添加自动扫描任务（一劳永逸）"><a href="#2-添加自动扫描任务（一劳永逸）" class="headerlink" title="2. 添加自动扫描任务（一劳永逸）"></a>2. 添加自动扫描任务（一劳永逸）</h3><p>如果不想每次手动扫描，可以设置定时任务让 Nextcloud 自动扫描。<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进入容器</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo docker <span class="built_in">exec</span> -it nextcloud bash</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装 cron 并添加定时任务（每5分钟扫描一次）</span></span><br><span class="line">apt-get update &amp;&amp; apt-get install -y cron</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;*/5 * * * * php /var/www/html/occ files:scan --all&quot;</span> | crontab -</span><br><span class="line">service cron start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>这样设置后，系统会每 5 分钟自动扫描一次，新文件会在 5 分钟内同步到网页端。</p><hr><h2 id="五、权限修复"><a href="#五、权限修复" class="headerlink" title="五、权限修复"></a>五、权限修复</h2><h3 id="Nextcloud-无法删除文件（宿主机直接复制文件）"><a href="#Nextcloud-无法删除文件（宿主机直接复制文件）" class="headerlink" title="Nextcloud 无法删除文件（宿主机直接复制文件）"></a>Nextcloud 无法删除文件（宿主机直接复制文件）</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进入容器检查文件所有权</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo docker <span class="built_in">exec</span> -it nextcloud-app-1 bash</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ls</span> -la /var/www/html/data/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 确保用户和组是 www-data，如果不对则修复</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">chown</span> -R www-data:www-data /var/www/html/data</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">exit</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="六、常用命令速查"><a href="#六、常用命令速查" class="headerlink" title="六、常用命令速查"></a>六、常用命令速查</h2><div class="table-container"><table><thead><tr><th style="text-align:left">用途</th><th style="text-align:left">命令</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:left">查看容器状态</td><td style="text-align:left"><code>docker ps</code></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">进入容器终端</td><td style="text-align:left"><code>sudo docker exec -it &lt;容器名&gt; bash</code></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">查看容器日志</td><td style="text-align:left"><code>docker logs &lt;容器名&gt;</code></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">重启容器</td><td style="text-align:left"><code>docker restart &lt;容器名&gt;</code></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">查看所有卷</td><td style="text-align:left"><code>docker volume ls</code></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">查看卷详情</td><td style="text-align:left"><code>docker volume inspect &lt;卷名&gt;</code></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">停止容器</td><td style="text-align:left"><code>docker stop &lt;容器名&gt;</code></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">删除容器</td><td style="text-align:left"><code>docker rm &lt;容器名&gt;</code></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:left">删除卷</td><td style="text-align:left"><code>docker volume rm &lt;卷名&gt;</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div>]]>
    </content>
